#Normalisation

UNF (group all data in one entity)
DB(Personnel number, Name, Date of birth, Lab code, Lab name, Research code, Research description, Research supervisor) 

1NF (all repeating and calculated groups are eliminated in individual tables, as all attributes should be atomic
Research code, description and supervisor are repeating fields

DB(Personnel number, Name, Date of birth, Research supervisor)
DB(Lab code, Lab name, Research code)	
DB(Research code, Research description)

2NF

DB(Personnel number, Name, Date of birth)
DB(Lab code, Lab name, Research code)
DB(Research code, Research description)

3NF
=2NF
